Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:34.49,sign_4317_1_Hatori,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Hatori
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.24,0:01:37.45,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to regret\N this later, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.74,0:01:42.53,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:50.17,sign_4705_4_Hatori_Chise,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Hatori Chise
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.75,0:01:56.09,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,With that, the contract is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.30,0:01:58.80,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hatori Chise-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.31,0:02:12.40,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Can you breathe all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:33.38,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.05,0:02:46.81,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,I'd heard rumors, but I've \Nnever seen one before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:51.77,Magus-internal/narrator,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,There are things that are \Nneither human nor inanimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.06,0:02:55.57,Magus-internal/narrator,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,They're different from the \Nones that I always see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:02:57.82,Magus-internal/narrator,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew things like this existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:13.00,Magus-internal/narrator,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:15.87,Magus-internal/narrator,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I just want somewhere to go home to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:19.09,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,This is the product you've \Nall been waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:23.01,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,A rare item, even among \Nour current offerings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:24.89,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Starting at 500,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:27.10,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,1,100,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:28.52,Default,C,0000,0000,0000,,1,500,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:29.81,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,1,800,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:31.31,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,2,000,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:32.81,Default,Z,0000,0000,0000,,Look there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:34.40,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Why is {\i1}he{\i0} here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:34.77,Magus-top,F,0000,0000,0000,,2,250,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:37.27,Default,Z,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he hated being around people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:36.36,Magus-top,A,0000,0000,0000,,2,250,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.36,0:03:37.94,Magus-top,A,0000,0000,0000,,2,250,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:40.03,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:43.49,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:51.04,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,5,000,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:58.09,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,It's decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:07.10,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,I will make you my apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.14,0:04:16.15,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,What's the deal with that creep?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:17.86,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:20.32,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare a reception room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:21.57,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:25.57,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,We will be receiving five million pounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:30.62,Magus-internal/narrator,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he, to want to spend \Nso much money on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:27.70,Magus-top,A,0000,0000,0000,,Age, fifteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:29.12,Magus-top,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Ethnicity, Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:32.54,Magus-top,A,0000,0000,0000,,She's docile, so she should \Nbe easy to discipline.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:36.71,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd see you at this auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:40.42,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,However, we must ask you\N to follow the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.42,0:04:41.76,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't wander onto the stage—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:44.22,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need your lecturing nor small talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:47.80,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,You, come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:52.98,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to keep your head down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:56.56,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Stand tall, and look forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:04:57.44,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:04:59.36,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:03.07,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be borrowing your lobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:04.07,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,By all means.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:14.16,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,What is he, a monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:17.25,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,He'll hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:18.54,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:22.59,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,He's neither a conman nor a sorcerer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.59,0:05:26.01,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,He's the real deal, a rarity\N in recent times.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:51.95,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe we let him have that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:53.33,Default,C,0000,0000,0000,,That Sleigh Beggy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:55.79,Magus-internal/narrator,C,0000,0000,0000,,Sleigh Beggy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:59.33,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,So you {\i1}can{\i0} see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:11.26,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You mean me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.85,0:06:15.06,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one here with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:16.35,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:25.44,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Chise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:27.49,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Hatori Chise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.53,0:06:30.11,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Elias.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:32.95,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Elias Ainsworth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:36.83,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, my puppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.34,0:06:51.55,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that you possess the sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:52.68,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,How fortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:55.26,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunate...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:57.60,Flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,She's too much of a burden to take in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:07:00.48,Flashback,B,0000,0000,0000,,What would people think if we gave \Nher to an orphanage, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.48,0:07:02.35,Flashback,C,0000,0000,0000,,She's being weird again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:03.61,Flashback,D,0000,0000,0000,,Creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:04.61,Flashback,E,0000,0000,0000,,She scares me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:07.61,Flashback,F,0000,0000,0000,,What a brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:15.33,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:20.08,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I've never once been fortunate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:26.13,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's see to it that you \Nfeel fortunate someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:35.35,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,I can't have you being so helpless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:42.56,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Dolls are fine, but I paid\N good money for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:48.78,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,You need to make yourself worth looking at.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:51.57,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:54.66,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Now, close your eyes and stand close to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:57.28,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,This may make you dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.91,0:08:01.08,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Nettles in the shadow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:05.29,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Ring of holly...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:12.22,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Thoroughly entangle the\Nbranches as a spider's web.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:14.26,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Thorns?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:20.35,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,You can open your eyes now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:36.91,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,As expected,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:38.24,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,we made it in one leap.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:41.33,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,This is my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.91,0:08:44.92,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,It's also your home, as of today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:47.50,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:48.92,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:51.05,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,How did we get here from \Ninside the building?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:54.51,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,This is west of London.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:56.89,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,A rural area on the outskirts of England.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:58.85,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,E-E-England?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:01.18,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,And what am I an "apprentice" of?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.18,0:09:03.27,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:05.60,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,You won't need that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:14.28,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,You've become a mage's apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.86,0:09:17.36,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,A mage?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:22.79,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,We're an endangered, \Nold-fashioned kind, mind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:30.34,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,I welcome you as my \Napprentice, Sleigh Beggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:34.97,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather... Chise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:46.56,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:47.60,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I can do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:49.23,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I know how to take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:50.15,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know how to use it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:53.03,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you're filthy, so I'll wash you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:56.86,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Come now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:09:59.87,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,You're not a kitten. Stop fussing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:03.91,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,You need to soak to your shoulders, \Nor you'll never be warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:05.66,Magus-internal/narrator,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,He saw everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.46,0:10:08.17,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Come out when you're warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:28.48,Magus-internal/narrator,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think I'd ever \Nget a proper bath again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:36.99,Flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever feel like giving up on life,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.99,0:10:41.57,Flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,why don't you try giving yourself \Nto someone who wants you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:11:00.22,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, I thought I smelled\N something delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:02.43,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's an adorable human girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:04.18,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Fairies?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:17.94,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose we'd be fairies, in human terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:21.24,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,You better not use such \N unrefined words for us, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:22.07,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:23.53,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Call us your neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:24.66,Default,C,0000,0000,0000,,Or your good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:27.58,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're a Sleigh Beggy, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:33.92,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,The Thorn Mage is so silly, taking \Nin a Sleigh Beggy as his apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:38.05,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Honey wine, more valuable than \Ngold coins of ancient times,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:41.26,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,more precious than any flower \Nof the land of fairies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:42.30,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:43.22,Default,C,0000,0000,0000,,Adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:44.93,Default,C,0000,0000,0000,,Our robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:50.98,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to become a mage, we'll \Ngive you all the help you need, my beloved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:55.90,Magus-internal/narrator,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Beloved?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:56.40,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Chise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:11:58.73,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:11:59.90,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,You're not overheated?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:02.28,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:05.12,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,so you don't need to come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:10.33,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,They're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:20.76,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Have something to eat and \Ndrink so you can relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.57,0:12:43.57,Magus-internal/narrator,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,It's like they really do welcome me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:46.82,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you have a lot of questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:49.08,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try to answer your questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:51.25,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be like a bedtime story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.66,0:12:54.08,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I saw fairies...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:56.96,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the ariels.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.96,0:12:59.21,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,They must have greeted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:01.96,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,They're attracted to anything new.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:03.67,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:09.05,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that you're a mage?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:11.02,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,It is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:23.78,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,So when you say "apprentice"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:27.36,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,I mean "apprentice," my puppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.49,0:13:32.04,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Sleigh Beggies are rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:34.41,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,I was very lucky today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:39.88,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,What is this "Sleigh Beggy"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:44.72,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,If I had to choose a word, a queen bee.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:49.89,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,You—or, your kind, Sleigh Beggies,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:54.39,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,are capable of attracting and \Nbinding all manner of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:57.23,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Specifically, fairies and mysteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:14:04.32,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,They're worker bees that are drawn to you \Nwhether the queen bee can see them or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.86,0:14:06.24,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she can't see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:12.20,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you can see them, but that's\N not common among your kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:18.87,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,They bring fortune and misfortune \Nupon the queen bee.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:21.29,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Misfortune?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:27.09,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Their kindness and favors don't \Nnecessarily benefit a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.68,0:14:31.93,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,However, to be loved by them means \Nthat you'll never be without assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:38.51,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,You need their help to do magic, \Nso it's an important trait to have.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:43.82,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,You'll surely become a great mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:49.32,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't mean I'll be \Nordering you around, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:52.95,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't have any right to refuse, do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:55.91,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:14:59.71,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,You're free to reconsider, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:03.21,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Becoming a mage is just\None path of countless many.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:08.55,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,You're like family to me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:10.88,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,You can depend on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.22,0:15:13.39,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Family?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:18.73,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,This is an adder stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:22.31,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,The hole formed naturally \Nat the bottom of a river.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:24.19,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,It'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:25.86,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:34.66,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:38.54,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,You must be tired,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.54,0:15:40.41,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,so you should turn in for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:44.00,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Would you please show her to her room?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.60,0:16:04.10,Magus-internal/narrator,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I even get a proper place to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:09.82,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Family...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:15.37,Magus-internal/narrator,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,It smells strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.16,0:16:19.04,Magus-internal/narrator,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the scent of grass?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:23.25,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Chise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:25.29,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Chise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:27.25,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Chise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:31.47,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Chise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:39.81,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,You're the... um, neighbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:42.73,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why don't we go for a midnight walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:44.81,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,There's a nice forest nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:46.69,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:48.82,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, it'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:50.82,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Just for a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:53.78,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Take a walk, tire yourself \Nout a little and sleep well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:55.95,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:09.67,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,What a hopeless child.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:13.38,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it'll make for a good lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:25.89,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.89,0:17:28.31,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's the trail we leave \Nafter we've passed by.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.31,0:17:30.48,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,You can see that, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:34.19,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chise, what's your family like?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:37.16,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.53,0:17:39.95,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I was taken in by a lot \Nof different relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:42.54,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Were those people kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.17,0:17:47.04,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Chise?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:53.88,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I might not have come here \Nif I'd come to love them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.59,0:17:55.72,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:10.15,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we've walked pretty far.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.15,0:18:12.57,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:15.19,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta go even further, if anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:19.87,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you don't need \Nto go back anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:25.45,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,We finally duped the Thorn Mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:26.71,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.71,0:18:31.71,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I need to take you back to our land, \Nor the others will get angry at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:36.09,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a lot easier than \Nliving in the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:37.42,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:39.22,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it just happens to be open.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.64,0:18:41.89,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,The Fairy Kingdom is past here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:45.39,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,A super fun world, just for you and us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:46.43,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.69,0:18:50.02,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:54.61,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.61,0:18:56.36,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Back where?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:18:58.65,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even have family waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:06.79,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,You might as well live a happy, \Ngiddy life on this side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:11.79,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:14.59,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I have no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:29.39,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Chise?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:30.89,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:36.40,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:38.24,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.24,0:19:42.32,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason you have \Nto go back to that house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:46.41,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,No one ever told me that I could be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:50.66,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,But that man told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.58,0:19:53.42,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I'm just a toy,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:55.67,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,even if he'll throw me out \Nwhen he's bored of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:20:02.47,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,he told me I was family, \Neven if it was just that once.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:04.68,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:12.44,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like my puppy has already \Nlearned where her den is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:14.73,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Elias.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:17.65,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Curses! How did you know where we were?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.65,0:20:20.19,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,She has a collar and a bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:22.74,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:24.82,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,I'll forgive you just this once.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:27.45,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, you'll be salamander food.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:31.08,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see if a half-baked loser \Nlike you can protect our robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:34.29,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to remind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:39.92,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,You can change your mind \Nwhenever you want, Chise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:46.76,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Chise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:52.35,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,That was a good experience, was it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:57.77,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Many of them make a habit of \Nseducing us with sweet words.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.15,0:21:00.57,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.99,0:21:02.82,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.49,0:21:07.78,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,No, I should have told you right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:13.25,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,That's my duty to you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:17.08,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,You're my apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.08,0:21:18.38,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Depend on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.79,0:21:20.13,Magus-internal/narrator,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,He's warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:24.51,Magus-internal/narrator,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems like he's tense—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.09,0:21:27.43,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.43,0:21:29.60,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy to get lost \Nin the forest at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.39,0:21:32.60,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.43,0:21:34.69,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,To our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.27,0:21:42.11,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,We'll need to fix up your \Narm when we get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.65,0:21:46.24,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,I can't have my future wife be scarred.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.95,0:21:52.08,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.45,0:21:54.04,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Who is who's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.04,0:21:56.08,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, have I not told you yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.83,0:22:01.16,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,I bought you to be my apprentice, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.47,0:22:13.43,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,but I also hope to make you my bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.44,0:22:19.81,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.41,0:23:58.08,Default,Elias,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we prepare for our honeymoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.08,0:23:58.70,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.20,0:24:02.37,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,A girl, departing for \NLondon with a sorcerer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.37,0:24:05.05,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,Unfamiliar towns, unfamiliar people.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.05,0:24:09.35,Default,Chise,0000,0000,0000,,The world offers a kind hand \Nto a lonely girl, but...
